                    <tr><td>embeddable - use directly from any JVM-friendly language</td></tr>
                    <tr class="advanced"><td>monitorable - advanced insight into database status</td></tr>
                    <tr class="enterprise"><td>robust - High Availability for read scaling and failover</td></tr>
                  </tbody>
                </table>
              </div>
