          </div>
          
        </div>
        
        <aside class="span4 sidebar">
          <div class="summary">
            <h2>Briefly</h2>
            <div class="well">
              <p>Neo4j is a <strong>graph</strong> database</p>
              <ul class="circle">
                      <li>the data model is a Property Graph</li>
                      <li>Nodes + Relationships, with Properties</li>
                      <li>Query with a traversal</li>
                      <li>Indexes for simple lookups</li>
              </ul>
              <p>Neo4j is a graph <strong>database</strong></p>
              <ul class="circle">
                      <li>reliable ACID transactions</li>
                      <li>scalable to billions of records</li>
                      <li>easily grokked REST API</li>
                      <li>high-performance HA clustering</li>
